      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>These letters set out the details of implementation funding payments to be made in the year 2020 to 2021 to support preparation for devolution of the adult education budget.</p>

<p>Payments will be made as section 31 demand led grants.</p>

<p>The Secretary of State for Education makes grant determinations under <a rel="external" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2003/26/section/31" class="govuk-link">section 31 of the Local Government Act 2003</a>.</p>
</div>

</div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 10 November 2020
